# KIBX / NIBMX — Codebase Analysis

**Nigeria International Bullion Market Exchange** — A full-stack digital gold trading marketplace headquartered in Kano, Nigeria.

---

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Clients"
        WEB["Web App<br/>(Vite + React)"]
        MOB["Mobile App<br/>(React Native / Expo)"]
    end
    subgraph "Backend"
        API["Express 5 API<br/>(27 route modules)"]
        MW["Middleware Layer<br/>(Auth, CSRF, Rate Limit)"]
    end
    subgraph "Infrastructure"
        DB["PostgreSQL<br/>(Neon DB)"]
        PAY["Paystack<br/>(Payments)"]
        KYC_SVC["Veriff<br/>(KYC)"]
        GOLD["Gold API<br/>(Live Pricing)"]
        EMAIL["Nodemailer<br/>(Email)"]
    end

    WEB --> API
    MOB --> API
    API --> MW
    API --> DB
    API --> PAY
    API --> KYC_SVC
    API --> GOLD
    API --> EMAIL
```

---

## Project Structure

| Directory | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `api/` | Express 5 backend — serverless on Vercel |
| `api/_routes/` | 27 route modules (auth, KYC, escrow, etc.) |
| `api/_lib/` | Shared libs: DB pool, middleware, security, gold pricing, KYC |
| `web/` | Vite + React frontend (62 pages, 15 components) |
| `mobile/` | React Native / Expo mobile app (9 screens) |
| `scripts/` | 18 migration, seed, and utility scripts |
| `__tests__/` | Jest + Supertest API tests |

---

## Backend (Express 5 API)

### Core Modules

The API entrypoint [index.mjs](file:///c:/Users/OMEN/Documents/kibx/api/index.mjs) bootstraps Express with:
- **Helmet** security headers (CSP, HSTS, frameguard, XSS filter)
- **CORS** whitelist (localhost, `kibx.vercel.app`, `nibmx.ng`)
- **Rate limiting** — 30 req/15min for auth, 60 for admin, 100 for general API
- **CSRF** double-submit cookie pattern
- **Feature flags** table (p2p_chat, price_alerts, escrow, kyc_upload, etc.)
- Auto-seeding of 14 staff accounts on startup

### Route Modules (27 files)

| Module | Responsibility |
|--------|---------------|
| `auth.mjs` | Register, login, JWT token flow |
| `2fa.mjs` | TOTP-based two-factor authentication |
| `kyc.mjs` | KYC document upload & verification (Veriff) |
| `aml.mjs` | Anti-money-laundering checks |
| `profile.mjs` | User profile management |
| `listings.mjs` | Gold listing CRUD |
| `marketplace.mjs` | Marketplace browsing, search, filters |
| `orders.mjs` | Order creation & management |
| `escrow.mjs` | Escrow payment holding & release |
| `payments.mjs` | Paystack payment initiation |
| `webhooks.mjs` | Paystack webhook handling |
| `gold.mjs` | Live gold pricing (24K, 22K, 18K) |
| `seller.mjs` | Seller dashboard & analytics |
| `buyer.mjs` | Buyer operations |
| `vault.mjs` | Gold vault storage management |
| `blockchain.mjs` | On-chain gold provenance tracking |
| `tokens.mjs` | Gold-backed token management |
| `tiers.mjs` | Cooperative tier system (5–50 members) |
| `agent.mjs` | Field agent management & commissions |
| `risk.mjs` | Risk scoring & analysis engine |
| `investment.mjs` | Investment portfolio management |
| `admin-lite.mjs` | Basic admin operations |
| `admin-super.mjs` | Full superadmin panel |
| `superadmin.mjs` | Platform-wide admin controls |
| `executive.mjs` | Executive-level reporting |
| `notifications.mjs` | Push notification delivery |

### Shared Libraries (`api/_lib/`)

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `db.mjs` | PostgreSQL connection pool (via `pg`) |
| `middleware.mjs` | JWT auth, role guards, CSRF, input sanitization, validation, feature flags, audit logging |
| `security.mjs` | CSRF token generation, 2FA enforcement, security event logging |
| `gold-pricing.mjs` | Real-time gold spot price fetching from external API |
| `kyc.mjs` | Veriff KYC integration |

---

## Database (PostgreSQL / Neon DB)

### Core Tables

**`users`** — Full user accounts with:
- Email, phone, password hash, full name
- `user_type` (buyer/seller/admin), `staff_role` (14 roles)
- KYC fields: `nin_verified`, `kyc_status`, `veriff_session_id`
- Location: state, company, avatar

**`listings`** — Gold marketplace listings with:
- Gold type: `Bullion`, `Nugget`, `Coin`, `Dust`, `Bar`
- Karat: `24K`, `22K`, `21K`, `18K`, `14K`
- Pricing: per-gram, total, currency (3-char)
- Assay: certified flag, lab name, report URL, purity %
- Shipping: `FOB`, `CIF`, `EXW`, `DDP`
- Status: `active`, `sold`, `reserved`, `expired`, `delisted`
- Origin: Nigerian state + LGA

### Additional Tables (via migrations)

The `scripts/` directory reveals many more tables:
- **`orders`**, **`escrow_transactions`** — Order & payment flow
- **`cooperative_tiers`**, **`tier_members`** — Cooperative membership
- **`agents`** — Field agent network
- **`vault_holdings`**, **`blockchain_records`** — Vault + provenance
- **`risk_scores`**, **`audit_log`** — Risk engine & audit trail
- **`feature_flags`** — Runtime feature toggles

