## Web Frontend (Vite + React)

### Stack
- **Vite** build tool, **React Router** for SPA routing
- **Lazy-loaded** code splitting for all 62 pages
- **i18n** — Full internationalization (English, Hausa, Arabic, French, Yoruba)
- **AuthContext** — JWT-based auth state management

### Page Categories

**Public pages:**
`Home`, `Marketplace`, `ListingDetail`, `LivePricing`, `MiningMap`, `AgentDirectory`, `Blockchain`

**Authenticated user pages:**
`Dashboard`, `BuyerDashboard`, `Orders`, `Cart`, `KYC`, `Profile`, `Chat`, `VaultDashboard`

**Staff role-based dashboards (14 roles):**

| Route | Dashboard | Role |
|-------|-----------|------|
| `/staff` | StaffDashboard | General staff |
| `/staff/md` | MDDashboard | Managing Director |
| `/staff/ceo` | CEODashboard | CEO |
| `/staff/cto` | CTODashboard | CTO |
| `/staff/investor` | InvestorDashboard | Investor |
| `/staff/ops` | OpsDashboard | Ops Manager |
| `/staff/accountant` | AccountantDashboard | Accountant |
| `/staff/logistics` | LogisticsDashboard | Logistics |
| `/staff/assay` | AssayDashboard | Assay Specialist |
| `/staff/kyc` | KYCOfficerDashboard | KYC Officer |
| `/staff/support` | SupportDashboard | Support Lead |
| `/staff/secretary` | SecretaryDashboard | Secretary |
| `/staff/tier-officer` | TierOfficerDashboard | Tier Officer |
| `/staff/mobilization` | MobilizationDashboard | Dir. Mobilization |

**Admin pages:**
`NormalAdmin`, `AdminPanel` (superadmin), `TierAdminDashboard`

**Specialized pages:**
`RiskAnalysis` (151KB — largest page), `StrategyHub`, `AgentDashboard`, `ApiDocs`

### Components (15 reusable)
`Navbar`, `Footer`, `AuthModal`, `BuyModal`, `ListingCard`, `ListingFormModal`, `GoldPriceTicker`, `MiniChart`

