## Mobile App (React Native / Expo)

### 9 Screens
`HomeScreen`, `MarketScreen`, `LoginScreen`, `ProfileScreen`, `SellerScreen`, `OrdersScreen`, `ChatScreen`, `KYCScreen`, `NotificationsScreen`

### Features
- Shared API client (`src/api.js`) pointing to the same backend
- Theme system (`src/theme.js`) with gold-accent branding
- Multi-language translations (English, Hausa, Arabic)
- Push notification support via Expo

---

## Deployment

- **Hosting**: Vercel (serverless)
- **API**: Single serverless function at `api/index.mjs` (10s max duration)
- **Frontend**: Vite build output from `web/dist/`
- **Rewrites**: `/api/*` → serverless function, `/*` → SPA fallback
- **Security headers**: HSTS, X-Frame-Options DENY, nosniff, strict referrer

---

## Key Business Features

1. **Multi-seller gold marketplace** with BMR/LBMA-standard assay certification
2. **Escrow payments** via Paystack — funds held until gold verified & shipped
3. **KYC/AML compliance** — Veriff identity verification + anti-money-laundering checks
4. **Cooperative tier system** — Group buying (5–50 members per tier)
5. **Gold vault storage** with blockchain-backed provenance tracking
6. **Gold-backed tokens** — Tokenized gold ownership
7. **Live gold pricing** — Real-time 24K/22K/18K spot prices
8. **Risk analysis engine** — Comprehensive risk scoring
9. **Field agent network** — Commission-based agent recruitment
10. **Investment portfolios** — Gold investment management
11. **14 staff role dashboards** — Full organizational hierarchy
12. **P2P chat** between buyers and sellers
13. **Mining map** — Nigerian gold mining locations
14. **Strategy hub** — Business intelligence & planning
